data.description: This charming cottage has everything you need for simple, private life! Master on main, cozy-but-spacious layout, "bonus" room to use as an office/sunroom/bedroom, lots of windows letting in light, hardwoods throughout, well flowing kitchen with lots of cabinet space, dual vanity bathroom, covered front AND back porch, and beautiful views of peaceful surrounding woods. This property won't last long!! Schedule your showing today!
